&lt;li&gt;0-2 years of full-time work experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Diploma/Degree in quantitative/technical field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail and accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reliable and trustworthy (handles sensitive financial data)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good problem-solving and communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
